{"tid":1353295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］如果用國徽做盾...","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:50:03.000Z","uid":281766,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c32d165991754dbf34b5c3455f6b465d0748d80f","tid":1353295,"uid":281766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"或者貼貼紙落盔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/A401!zh-Hant-HK@2017-02-15T00:00:00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2FA401%21zh-Hant-HK%402017-02-15T00%3A00%3A00&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUitfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=f6e393b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/A401!zh-Hant-HK@2017-02-15T00:00:00</a><br />\n<br />\n嚴格黎講示威並非「日常生活的陳設或布置」（見條文），所以不在條例所列的禁止事項下。<br />\n但如果任何人「故意以焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗或國徽，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第5級罰款及監禁3年。」<br />\n即班狗係不能打盾？<br />\n<br />\n禁止將國旗、國徽用作某些用途<br />\n(1)國旗或其圖案不得展示或使用於 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)商標或廣告；<br />\n(b)私人喪事活動；或<br />\n(c)行政長官以規定限制或禁止展示或使用國旗或其圖案的其他場合或場所。<br />\n(2)國徽或其圖案不得展示或使用於 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)商標或廣告；<br />\n(b)日常生活的陳設或布置；<br />\n(c)私人慶弔活動；或<br />\n(d)行政長官以規定限制或禁止展示或使用國徽或其圖案的其他場合或場所。"},{"pid":"42809a4728a7736c592504bcac6e5700d4417e5f","tid":1353295,"uid":32861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721宣言</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUitfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=d923bdbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n條片只有<span style=\"color: green;\">3000views</span> <br />\n但留言勁多5毛 某程度證明有用<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手留言 引啲5毛一齊推上Youtube熱門"},{"pid":"5fae615872960c029022f38a6aba417f26cfda08","tid":1353295,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:59:05.000Z","msg":"某些廟宇甚至有掛五星紅旗<img src=\"/assets